  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, fish sauce, garlic, oregano, thyme, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the fish fillets to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread the marinated fish onto the soaked wooden skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Place the skewers on the grill and cook for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Add the bay leaves to the grill and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Remove the skewers from the grill and serve immediately.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley or thyme, if desired."
  ],
